text: Hi all, my name is Nicole, I'm a UX Researcher working with the Content Tools teams here at HubSpot. We're starting to explore local CMS development workflows and I was hoping you all could give me a couple minutes of your time and fill out this quick survey, <https://www.research.net/r/22LXYN2>. We'd love to know more about some of your processes to make sure we're creating tools that are useful to you. Thanks so much!
